title: Mermaid Test All Diagrams
author: asophila
created: 20260427
modified: 20260427
tags: [[mermaid test]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This tiddler tests every diagram type supported by Mermaid 11.14.0 in the mermaid-tw5 plugin.

!! Flowchart

<$mermaid text="
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Decision}
    B -->|Yes| C[Action 1]
    B -->|No| D[Action 2]
    C --> E[End]
    D --> E
"/>

!! Sequence Diagram

<$mermaid text="
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant B as Bob
    A->>B: Hello Bob
    B-->>A: Hi Alice
    A->>B: How are you?
    Note right of B: Bob thinks
    B-->>A: Fine, thanks!
"/>

!! Class Diagram

<$mermaid text="
classDiagram
    class Animal {
        +String name
        +int age
        +makeSound() void
    }
    class Dog {
        +String breed
        +fetch() void
    }
    class Cat {
        +purr() void
    }
    Animal <|-- Dog
    Animal <|-- Cat
"/>

!! State Diagram

<$mermaid text="
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Running : start
    Running --> Idle : stop
    Running --> Error : fail
    Error --> Idle : reset
    Idle --> [*] : shutdown
"/>

!! Entity Relationship

<$mermaid text="
erDiagram
    CUSTOMER ||--o{ ORDER : places
    ORDER ||--|{ LINE_ITEM : contains
    CUSTOMER {
        string name
        string email
    }
    ORDER {
        int id
        date created
    }
    LINE_ITEM {
        string product
        int qty
    }
"/>

